meanings: Interjection (질문에 대한 답으로) 네, 응, 그래(요)
Interjection (남이 방금 한 말에 동의하여) 네, 응, 맞아[그래](요)
Youth Exchange Scheme for Europe(유럽 청년 교류 계획).
A confirmation used only by the thugest o' thugs.
An exclaimation of joy or excitement. see also woohoo, wahoo, score, yay

In recent years, it has become a phenomenon to congratulate or acknowledge one's presence by saying Yes and then their last name. Usually done by those who partake in the same sport. However, let it be known that if someone does something particularly daring or out of the ordinary, one may say Ye...
